name: Minimal Tokyo #004
description:
Tokyo, an infinitely bright, sometimes confusing city. 
Yet sometimes silent and distant when reduced to the minimal
A silent abstraction, a place to dream. 
Timeless: it was, it is, and it will be.

2017-21 NOIZE
An animated version of a series of BNW photos taken with Nokia 1020
Original Sound Design by Bill Tribble
